---
<section class="swamp-path" id="roadmap">
  <div class="swamp-mist"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="path-header">
      <h2 class="text-gradient">SWAMP PATH</h2>
      <p>The journey to total ogre domination.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="zig-zag-path">
      <div class="path-line"></div>
      
      <!-- Phase 1 -->
      <div class="path-node node-left">
        <div class="node-marker">01</div>
        <div class="node-content glass-card">
          <h3>THE SWAMPING</h3>
          <p>Initial launch on Solana. Organic community takeover. First layering event and $SHREK propagation.</p>
          <span class="node-status active">IN PROGRESS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2 -->
      <div class="path-node node-right">
        <div class="node-marker">02</div>
        <div class="node-content glass-card">
          <h3>ONION LAYERS</h3>
          <p>Donkey-approved ecosystem growth. Major CEX listings. First wave of Ogre NFTs.</p>
          <span class="node-status">UPCOMING</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 3 -->
      <div class="path-node node-left">
        <div class="node-marker">03</div>
        <div class="node-content glass-card">
          <h3>FARQUAAD FALL</h3>
          <p>Complete meme-fi dominance. DAO governance active. Infinite swamp expansion.</p>
          <span class="node-status">UPCOMING</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .swamp-path {
    padding: 10rem 0;
    background: #050505;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .path-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 8rem;
  }

  .path-header h2 { font-size: 4rem; }

  .zig-zag-path {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .path-line {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 4px;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--primary), #000);
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .path-node {
    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .node-left { justify-content: flex-start; }
  .node-right { justify-content: flex-end; }

  .node-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: #000;
    border: 3px solid var(--primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(164, 198, 57, 0.4);
  }

  .node-content {
    width: 42%;
    padding: 3rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: 0.3s;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: rgba(164, 198, 57, 0.05);
  }

  .node-content:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    background: rgba(164, 198, 57, 0.1);
    border-color: var(--primary);
  }

  h3 { color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .node-status {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .node-status.active {
    color: var(--primary);
    opacity: 1;
    animation: flash 1s infinite alternate;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .path-line { left: 30px; }
    .node-marker { left: 30px; transform: none; width: 40px; height: 40px; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    .node-content { width: calc(100% - 80px); margin-left: 80px; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .node-left, .node-right { justify-content: flex-start; }
  }
</style>
